    "TraditionalChinese": "農作收成"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A rubbery, luminescent sac harvested from <span class=\"name name-technology\">underwater</span> <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Candle Kelp</span> plants.<br><br>Agricultural science has not yet tamed the Candle Kelp. As such, these sacs cannot be farmed.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种弹性冷光液囊，可从<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">烛光藻</span>植物中收获。<br><br>农业科学目前还未培育烛光藻。同样，这些液囊也无法种植。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种弹性冷光液囊，可从<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">烛光藻</span>植物中收获。<br><br>农业科学目前还未培育烛光藻。同样，这些液囊也无法种植。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "自<span class=\"name name-technology\">水底</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">蠟燭巨藻</span>植物上取得的彈性發光囊袋。<br><br>以目前的農業科學技術，還無法人工栽種蠟燭巨藻。因此，這種囊袋無法透過耕種取得。"
  },
